metadata.name: Crown
metadata.description:
Unnamed peaks of Karakoram. Charakusa valley is situated in the heart of Karakoram and is surrounded by magnificient mountains which haven't been named yet. They all provide unique opportunity for rock climbing.

Took this photo from Saicho Campsite 12 days of trekking and climbing to capture these giants in the best possible conditions. Grateful for the experience and the ability to share it with you.

Mountain Range: Karakoram  
Country: Pakistan  
Season: Winter  
Artist: Artbysalman  
Edition: 1/1
